    "en": "Lets combine your previous challenges! With a few minor changes of course, you gotta use SMGs and Shotguns in certain calibers now, 9mm for SMGs and 12 Gauge for Shotguns, you think you'll manage it? Report back to me when you are done, good luck soldier."
